Class JFXChipView<T>

  • java.lang.Object

    public class JFXChipView<T>
extends javafx.scene.control.Control
    JFXChipArea is the material design implementation of chip Input. An easy way to manage chips in a text area component with an x to omit the chip.
    Since:
    2018-02-01
